    heroImage: "/images/articles/wellbeing-at-work/hero.jpeg",
    body: [
      { type: "sideBySide", imageSide: "right", image: { src: "/images/articles/wellbeing-at-work/hero.jpeg", alt: "" }, content: [{ type: "heading", level: 2, text: "Wellbeing at Work" }, { type: "paragraph", text: "We are passionate about the wellbeing of our team and creating a happy, healthy working environment for all. Ridgeview’s world leading wine and the wellness of our staff will always go hand-in-hand." }, { type: "paragraph", text: "Here’s how and why…" }] },
      { type: "sideBySide", imageSide: "left", image: { src: "/images/articles/wellbeing-at-work/inline-1.webp", alt: "The Roberts Family Ridgeview Wine Estate English sparkling wine Sussex England" }, content: [{ type: "heading", level: 2, text: "OUR FAMILY ETHOS" }, { type: "paragraph", text: "We are proud to be a second-generation family business and each member of our team becomes an extended part of that. Ridgeview were delighted to win ‘Best London and South-East Family Business’ in the [Family Business United Awards](https://familybusinessunited.com/) in 2021. This is testament to our commitment to empowering our staff to thrive in every aspect of their lives." }] },
      { type: "sideBySide", imageSide: "right", image: { src: "/images/articles/wellbeing-at-work/inline-2.webp", alt: "Ridgeview Wine Estate English sparkling wine Sussex England" }, content: [{ type: "heading", level: 2, text: "WE CELEBRATE TOGETHER" }, { type: "paragraph", text: "Ridgeview’s lively social committee dream up inventive ways for our team to socialise and have fun, in and outside of work." }, { type: "paragraph", text: "From paddle boarding to wine and spirits tastings, a community beach-clean to football friendlies, we are never short on ideas or enthusiasm to socialise and celebrate together!" }, { type: "paragraph", text: "We run a number of charitable initiatives as a team, like our staff raffles, foodbank donations and annual activity challenge, a charity initiative masterminded by our CEO, Tamara Roberts." }, { type: "paragraph", text: "Our team set personal activity goals which Ridgeview rewards by donating to a monthly charity of choice when they hit their target together." }] },
      { type: "sideBySide", imageSide: "left", image: { src: "/images/articles/wellbeing-at-work/inline-3.webp", alt: "Ridgeview Wine Estate English sparkling wine Sussex England" }, content: [{ type: "heading", level: 2, text: "HEALTH AND WELLNESS" }, { type: "paragraph", text: "Ridgeview has developed strong employee support networks." }, { type: "paragraph", text: "We encourage walk-and-talk meetings around the vineyard and offer a [Cycle-to-Work scheme](https://www.cyclescheme.co.uk/employers) to promote an active lifestyle that gives back to the planet." }, { type: "paragraph", text: "We have a team of trained mental health first aiders in the workplace and host coffee mornings providing a space to check in, chat and connect." }, { type: "paragraph", text: "Our team can access free, confidential and compassionate support through our [Employee Assistance Programme](https://www.healthassured.org/). We offer an annual [Wellbeing MOT](https://midsussex.westsussexwellbeing.org.uk/topics/wellbeing-at-work/wellbeing-at-work-employers) to empower our staff to reach their own health, wellness and lifestyle goals." }] },
      { type: "sideBySide", imageSide: "right", image: { src: "/images/articles/wellbeing-at-work/inline-4.webp", alt: "Ridgeview Head Office" }, content: [{ type: "heading", level: 2, text: "OUR CULTURE" }, { type: "paragraph", text: "We are a vibrant, diverse and dynamic team, with a caring culture of social responsibility who believe in doing business for good. We offer a [payroll giving scheme](https://www.charitablegiving.co.uk/) and will be launching Volunteering Days in 2022, providing staff with paid time off to take part in charitable activities close to their hearts." }, { type: "paragraph", text: "Ridgeview offers flexible working and part-time patterns to support a healthy work-life balance so our team can thrive in all aspects of their lives." }, { type: "paragraph", text: "We live and breathe a family ethos, valuing all of our staff as individuals, with a unique story and an important role to play." }] },
      { type: "heading", level: 2, text: "Discover More" },
      { type: "image", src: "/images/articles/wellbeing-at-work/inline-5.webp", alt: "Ridgeview Wine Estate vineyards" },
      { type: "heading", level: 3, text: "Join Our Team" },
      { type: "image", src: "/images/articles/wellbeing-at-work/inline-6.webp", alt: "Ridgeview Wine Estate award-winning English sparkling wine Sussex England" },
      { type: "heading", level: 3, text: "Inspiring the next Generation" },
      { type: "image", src: "/images/articles/wellbeing-at-work/inline-7.webp", alt: "Harvest at Ridgeview Wine Estate Sussex England" },
      { type: "heading", level: 3, text: "Diversity and Inclusion" },
    ],
